<strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">Animaciones</span></strong><br /><br />Secuencia para hacer a un actor ejecutar una animación (proveniente de los archivos de animación):<br />Paso 1: cargar la animación<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">04ED: load_animation &quot;bd_fire&quot; <br />repeat<br />wait 0 ms<br />until 04EE: animation &quot;bd_fire&quot; loaded</code>Hacemos que el actor ejecute la animación:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">0605: actor 40@ perform_animation_sequence &quot;wash_up&quot; IFP_file &quot;bd_fire&quot; 4.0 loop 1 0 0 0 time -1</code>Liberar la animación cargada:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">04EF: release_animation &quot;bd_fire&quot;</code><br />Aqui se puede saber más sobre cómo funciona el opcode 0605:<br /><a href="http://www.gtamodding.com/index.php?title=0605" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.gtamodding.com/index.php?title=0605</a><br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">Todo sobre Garages</span></strong><br />02FA: set_garage &#039;MICHDR&#039; type 5<br /><a href="http://www.gtamodding.com/index.php?title=Garage#Types_of_Garages" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.gtamodding.com/index.php?title=Garage#Types_of_Garages</a><br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">El codigo crear &quot;Coronas&quot; (racing checkpoints)</span></strong><br />024F: create_corona_with_radius [flt1] type [int1] lensflares [int2] with_color [int3] [int4] [int5] at [flt2] [flt3] [flt4] <br /><a href="http://www.gtamodding.com/index.php?title=024F" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.gtamodding.com/index.php?title=024F</a><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />EDIT: Probar este opcode PERO YA<br />0235: NOP 1 #BALLAS1 #BALLAS2<br />0235: set_gang_models 1 to #BALLAS1 #BALLAS2 // NOP<br />0236: set_gang_vehicles 0 to #GREENWOO // NOP<br /><br /><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">Como cambiar el skin del player</span></strong><br />En GTAIII:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">01F5: $PLAYER_ACTOR = create_emulated_actor_from_player $PLAYER_CHAR <br />if 8118:&nbsp; &nbsp;not actor $PLAYER_ACTOR dead <br />then<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; 0352: set_actor $PLAYER_ACTOR skin_to &#039;FLAN&#039; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; while 8248:&nbsp; &nbsp;not model #NULL available <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; wait 0 <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; end<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; if 8118:&nbsp; &nbsp;not actor $PLAYER_ACTOR dead <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; then 0353: refresh_actor $PLAYER_ACTOR<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; end<br />end</code><br />En GTAVC:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">???</code>Nota: aún no sé si cada línea de lo que se vé allí es necesario, no he optimizado.<br /><br /><strong>GTAIII Weapon numbers</strong><br /><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">Citar</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote">0 - unarmed<br />1 - bat<br />2 - pistol<br />3 - uzi<br />4 - shotgun<br />5 - AK47<br />6 - M16<br />7 - sniper<br />8 - rocket launcher<br />9 - flamethrower<br />10 -molotov coctail<br />11 -bomb</blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div><br /><a href="http://www.ref3.gta.mendelsohn.de/Ref_actortypes.html" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">GTAIII Actortypes (Incompleto)</a><br />
